{"tid":1799854,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"江永祥: 軍裝截停便衣人員屬溝通誤會","createTime":"2019-12-27T09:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T01:45:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":44,"dislike":362,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"5d521cf1820ee9d5c7387b0a63f31fd741efa895","tid":1799854,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥說，警方收到線報，知道有人昨日會在大埔超級城鬧事，於是派便衣警員到場。他說，有人進入餐廳搗亂，警方派人進入商場，當時環境混亂，人員要控制場面，於是截停一些人，期間有軍裝人員截停過1名便衣人員，最初溝通有誤會，很快就認清身分。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">江永祥表示，昨日下午2時半左右，有人到餐廳聚集，被職員拒絕進入後，經側門入內搗亂，有4人涉嫌阻差辦公及襲警等被捕，令他想起在反黑組工作時，黑社會騷擾不肯交保護費的店舖。江永祥說，這些便衣人員埋伏式行動，是針對情報去做，事前不會告訴他人，亦沒有理由在行動前通知商場。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2019-12-27 17:07:12"},{"pid":"4eba1b894b58c1cc831598caaafb3ff9582a85d5","tid":1799854,"uid":240362,"like":254,"dislike":1,"score":253,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"江永祥咁嘅樣都做過反黑組<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485fe28bfaa4517d618e27105fab3d5ff6f68424","tid":1799854,"uid":274161,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"原來截停需要箍頸同用警棍<br />\n【有片】防暴怒打便衣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/apHtoMU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/apHtoMU</a>"},{"pid":"ff57421fd5dbcd756fb26acfbe6998940db379b3","tid":1799854,"uid":60129,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"「屌自己友」"},{"pid":"a018d0e8919015a887712e48ad87a6226ea71b6c","tid":1799854,"uid":1767,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"咁攞棍毆呢 又係截停同控制場面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ee7f5073ffcef1c646ca1c0e1f438d51e1f4fe","tid":1799854,"uid":55914,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"cit